edu.udel.cis.taschd.course

Class Course

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.udel.cis.taschd.course.Course
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Course>

    public class Course
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Course>

    The Course represents static attributes of a Course. It specifies the attributes belongs to a Course. It hides the details on the internal representation of Course objects including offerings in a specific semester.

    Course uses module time and skill.

      • compareTo

        public int compareTo(Course that)

        The order is determined by first comparing prefix. If prefix are equal, courseCode is compared to break the tie. If courseCode is equal, courseName is compared to break the tie. If courseName is equal, both course objects are equal.

        Specified by:
        compareTo in interface java.lang.Comparable<Course>
